{"tid":156553,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大 美 人 嚴 選 17 年 第 一 季 5 大 死 唔 斷 氣 藝 人 ！","createTime":"2017-03-14T21:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T05:10:12.000Z","uid":53178,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b008865142d20247a1293745c848497154a812","tid":156553,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T21:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1.  關楚耀</strong></span><br />\n著名唱片監製關維麟個仔，可惜錯誤同「燈神」譚詠麟上契，09年藏毒由歌手變成道友，從此遭人唾棄。父幹下，道友耀近年間唔中都會唱歌同拍戲吊命，但只限於「喜愛夜蒲」級爛片。由於形象崩壞，近年道友耀索性走余文樂式老mk style，可惜已被人遺忘，賣肉後連半滴西水都呃唔到，令人不勝其煩。近日推出新歌，老是常出現。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2.  鄧穎芝</strong></span><br />\n樂壇賓妹、輻射版鄭融。自從有樂壇小強紀錄以來，一直榜上有名，死唔斷氣！上年出現喺viuTV《G1格鬧會》後，一直不斷消費節目名氣，可悲又可笑。今年推出多首連名都up唔出嘅新歌，又喺facebook表示希望今年可以遇到一首好似苦情人，大家都喜歡嘅歌，實在令人捧腹大笑！仲想翻身，天真過阿嬌！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26anCJV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26anCJV.jpg&h=a4b75411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3.  譚詠麟</strong></span><br />\n譚校長真係好煩！先有成隻吸血鬼咁痴住eason，合唱災難式電音歌曲《明日何其多》；後有祝賀曹星如連勝係「為所有中國人爭光」，呢隻老妖成日揀人抽陽氣，唔怪得可以死唔斷氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4.  吳業坤</strong></span><br />\n攞完男歌手獎後囂張跋扈，次年馬上被網民唾棄，只能急急腳回歸大台懷抱，拍劇吊命重新入屋，可惜最受歡迎男歌手只獲演出配角，最近在劇集《迷》嘅演技更加係令人發笑，拍在田蕊妮身邊連棋子都不如，九線藝人永遠都係九線藝人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>5.  洪卓立</strong></span><br />\n今年推出新歌《帶著骨灰去旅行》，自嘲is ok，但不斷消費「死訊」就會由幽默變成煩。Furthermore，要紅一早紅咗啦，你睇下你公司俾幾多資源你就知...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/794E21F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F794E21F.jpg&h=11c74843&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c50fc5ccff1f160a4d10bbd545e1573c15c0560","tid":156553,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T21:39:08.000Z","msg":"5個唔夠喉"},{"pid":"154d82dbe9feb73c671d3ab2f76b06b5a8528ce2","tid":156553,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T23:57:09.000Z","msg":"joey、汪阿姐、阿叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84a323f8a22906bfbdddebbe216ada292fc846e","tid":156553,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:00:26.000Z","msg":"重點係譚伯,呢件嘢真係累人累物"},{"pid":"a8612935a9dc7609280eefb429ca829ce3a79584","tid":156553,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:01:27.000Z","msg":"送禮勤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要爭獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce7ad5d69ead5abafc71cc897374241bc03fc5c","tid":156553,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ea514b6fcc678068f08379cb189b264debd5d1","tid":156553,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c032411fa26f02b9ae3b6ddad27535c56252075","tid":156553,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T03:26:46.000Z","msg":"2好慘 完全係行出街唔會有人認得果d<br />\n個格又衰 十足鄭融一樣 八婆格"},{"pid":"2bb8290b5a7a4cec3db4b7068600205f40c53d5a","tid":156553,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2好慘 完全係行出街唔會有人認得果d<br />\n個格又衰 十足鄭融一樣 八婆格</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://entretenimento.r7.com/blogs/alvaro-leme/files/2015/08/&Eacute;-tudo-culpa-do-Aecio.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fentretenimento.r7.com%2Fblogs%2Falvaro-leme%2Ffiles%2F2015%2F08%2F%C3%89-tudo-culpa-do-Aecio.gif&h=82f8bec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38a4bb640459814fefb70c69